                            <comment id="115922" author="adilger" created="Tue, 19 May 2015 18:10:44 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;James, could you please submit a patch to re-enable this test, and have it run the test a bunch of times to see if it is passing?  I suspect that this is only an intermittent failure, so we don&apos;t want to enable it with only a single passing test run.  See &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1867&quot; title=&quot;replay-single test_89: @@@@@@ FAIL: 4 blocks leaked&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-1867&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-1867&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; for more details.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
